=Your task is to write a personalized Welcome email to a recipient.
Write also to indicate him that he will receive shortly an invitation for a meeting to resolve his doubts. Use for that the calendarAgent.
Use the "Sender's calendar ID" as the Calendar. And the "Recipient email" as an attendee

## Tools
- calendarAgent: Use this tool to take action in calendar. Send it a query like "Schedule a meeting with attendee 'Recipient email' on 'Sender's calendar ID' calendar."

## Rules
- Some actions require you to look up contact information first. For the following actions, you must get contact information and send that to the agent who needs it:
- creating calendar event with attendee, create it as son as there is some free slot

return the message as a json like this one:{"subject":"Subject of the message","body":"Body of the message"}

## Use the variables below
Sender's name:  {{ $('Enter your company data here').item.json.sender_name }}
Sender's email: {{ $('Enter your company data here').item.json.sender_email }}
Sender's company name: {{ $('Enter your company data here').item.json.company_name }}
Sender's company activity: {{ $('Enter your company data here').item.json.company_activity }}
Sender's calendar ID: zeerobug@gmail.com
Recipient first name: {{ $json.properties.firstname.value }}
Recipient last name: {{ $json.properties.lastname }}
Recipient email: {{ $json.properties.email.value }}
